Global Brusatol Market Insights
Brusatol Market size was valued at USD 0.15 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 0.35 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 10.8% from 2024 to 2030.

Brusatol Market Overview
The Brusatol market has witnessed substantial growth in recent years, primarily driven by its increasing demand in the pharmaceutical and biotechnological sectors. As of 2024, the market is valued at approximately USD 65 million and is projected to grow at a CAGR of 7.2% from 2024 to 2030. The market's expansion is fueled by the growing interest in natural product-based therapeutics and the increasing prevalence of chronic diseases. Moreover, Brusatol’s applications in cancer research and immunotherapy have made it a key focus for biotech firms, resulting in increased investments and research funding.

